論文名稱：戰後印尼華人企業集團發展與政商關係之研究  頁數：141           校(院)所組別：淡江大學東南亞研究所碩士班           畢業時間及提要別：九十一學年度第二學期  碩士學位論文提要           研究生：周黃俊達                        指導教授：龔宜君 博士           關鍵字：印尼  華人  企業集團  政商關係           論文提要內容：           　　本論文是以『政商關係』的角度為出發點，來探討印尼華人企業集團的發展過程。首先，是就印尼軍．政官員與華人資本家的互動過程中，來分析印尼政商關係產生的緣起，並嘗試就國內．外環境的變遷因素，來瞭解其對政商關係的影響；其次，是分析第二次世界大戰後（印尼獨立）至現今，隨著執政者的更替，其政商關係對於印尼華人企業集團所扮演的角色，又有何差異性存在；最後，以政商關係對於華人企業集團發展的影響做為本文的結論。           　　事實上，在研究的過程中，可以瞭解到－印尼是存在著三種政商關係的發展，即特許性政商關係．裙帶性政商關係、阿裡巴巴政商關係。而此三種政商關係於1945-1965年代，是一種由下而上之利益交換的性質，1966-1998年代，即呈現出由上而下之侍從關係的性質，至1998年代以後，卻轉換為具有雙向合作透明化性質的政商關係。           　　就本文的結論方面，綜合地發現－戰後印尼政商關係對於華人企業集團的重要性，呈現出『∩型曲線』的發展。此外，不同類型之政商關係，對於華人企業集團發展，確實有直接性的幫助，並且其影響程度，呈現出同心圓的結果。

Title of Thesis：                                        Total Pages：141           The Business Groups of Chinese in Indonesia and Cronyism：1945-2003           Name of Institute：           Tamkang University，Graduate Institute of Southeast Asia Studies           Graduate Date：June，2003                      Degree Conferred：Master           Name of Student：Chou Huang，Chun-Ta          Advisor：Dr. Kung，I-Chun           Key Words：Indonesia，Chinese，Business Groups，Cronyism           Abstract：               The dissertation starts from the point of view on “cronyism” to be researched on the development of the Indonesia Chinese business groups .Firstly，it points out the analysis made for the causes of Indonesia cronyism would be related to the interaction among Indonesia army，government officials and Chinese capitalist，and it makes sense of the results of “cronyism” through the changing factors under the domestic or foreign circumstances. Secondly，it indicates that “cronyism” has played a key role in Indonesia Chinese business groups after the Second World War (Indonesia Independence）till the present time，and exists the differences，following the alternating government. Lastly，it makes a conclusion of “cronyism” which has its effects on the development of Chinese capitalists.               In fact，from the research，it can be understood that in Indonesia are three kinds of “cronyism”—concession rights crony，patron-client，and Ali-baba crony. Among the three kinds of “cronyism”，one of them was the quality of exchanging benefits from the lower to the upper，dated from the periods between 1945 and 1965；during the periods of 1966 and 1998，it showed the character of patron-client crony from the upper to the lower，and after the year 1998，it has turned to the transparent nature of “cronyism” with two-way cooperation.               At the conclusion of the research，synthetically it prove that after the war the development of the important Indonesia cronyism for the Chinese business group has the shape of the curve“∩”.Besides，the different types of “cronyism” for the development of Chinese business group actually have much direct help and their effects could make the center-point circle as the results.

